-[GRUNTING]

04:19.302 --> 04:24.655
-[SIRENS WAILING]

04:44.849 --> 04:49.593
-[BREATHING HEAVILY]

05:00.082 --> 05:02.127
-CAROLINE: LET ME HELP YOU.

05:02.258 --> 05:05.130
-NO! I SAID I DIDN'T NEED
ANY HELP!
-CAROLINE: I'M A LIFEGUARD.

05:05.261 --> 05:06.218
TAKE THE CAN!

05:07.219 --> 05:09.657
PLEASE, TAKE THE CAN AND
LET ME FLOAT YOU IN ON IT.

05:09.787 --> 05:11.702
LISTEN TO ME! IT'S ALL RIGHT.

05:15.619 --> 05:16.925
COME ON.

05:18.579 --> 05:20.494
-I'M HERE, I'VE GOT HIM.

05:20.624 --> 05:22.757
-OKAY, OKAY.

05:22.887 --> 05:25.020
-IT'S OKAY, LET'S GO.

05:25.150 --> 05:27.152
-LOGAN: YOU ALL
RIGHT? GET HIS NECK.

05:42.603 --> 05:44.126
-NO PULSE.

05:47.216 --> 05:51.263
-ONE, TWO, THREE, FOUR, FIVE.

05:53.135 --> 05:57.705
